.A–B. Male habitus (AMNH_IZC 00217588): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C–F. Male right palp: C. Ventral view. D. Prolateral view. E. Retroventral view. F. Retrolateral view. Scale bars: A–B: 2mm; C–D: 200µm; E–F: 500µm.
